    <item>
      <title>TikTok 称法律站在一边，准备对抗美国禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/tiktok-says-law-is-on-its-side-as-it-prepares-to-fight-us-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok表示，美国国会周二晚间通过的立法将迫使其中国母公司出售其股份，否则该应用程序将在美国面临全面禁令，该立法“违宪”，该公司将在法庭上提出质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/tiktok-says-law-is-on-its-side-as-it-prepares-to-fight-us-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉股东要求法官维持马斯克在特拉华州的薪酬斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/tesla-shareholder-asks-judge-to-keep-musk-pay-fight-in-delaware</link>
      <description><![CDATA[成功挑战联合创始人埃隆·马斯克 560 亿美元薪酬方案的特斯拉公司股东正在请求特拉华州法院下令禁止马斯克在德克萨斯州再次就此事提起诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/tesla-shareholder-asks-judge-to-keep-musk-pay-fight-in-delaware</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:20:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
